    {
      "id": "b47d3a09-40ff-41c8-8252-3ab6921b487c",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Paper uses NLP to predict the performance of students at the end of a course. The model uses historical enrollment data and course descriptions to predict the potential grade of a student in a course. The authors use BERT to analyse the text and create course description embeddings. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "b47d3a09-40ff-41c8-8252-3ab6921b487c",
        "parent": {
