    {
      "id": "6d7f4712-6986-4a41-8f9f-afd49e1de423",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Moreover, the author creates a student knowledge profile that is based on the descriptions of the courses the student has already attended AND the student’s respective performance on that course. The approach had soime promise but still has plenty of room for improvement according to the authors. ",
